cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and dependency parsing. The use of neural network architecture also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The combination of bidirectional LSTM and CNN also suggests that it could belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the use of character-level representations could suggest that it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition).
